{
  "title":"Brilliant Idea",
  "date":"2006-06-29 CST",
  "origin":"Funny Logic",
  "url":"text-brilliant-idea",
  "author":"Ryan X. Charles"
}



			
				<p>&#8220;I have an idea,&#8221; said the first designer. &#8220;We&#8217;ll base the new logo on itself.&#8221;</p>

				<p>&#8220;That&#8217;ll never work,&#8221; said the second designer. &#8220;It&#8217;s like using a trash can to throw itself away.&#8221;</p>

				<p>&#8220;I do that all the time,&#8221; said the person who wasn&#8217;t there.</p>

		
		

